<h2>Coated or furry tongue, Thick saliva or mucus and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms coated or furry tongue, thick saliva or mucus and white patches on tongue including Constipation (child), Constipation (adult), and Dehydration (Children).</p>
